<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śākēṁgākṣīguṇakṣamāparimitē <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/><unclear>śyā</unclear>ṁ bhṛguvāsarē nṛhareyē svēṣṭāptayē cāmarē <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> bhūtyai śrīnarasi
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṁhyadēvanṛpatēssāmaṁtarāyōdiśātsa narayaṇasaṁjñaka sta
<lb n="4" break="no"/>nūbhavōnaṁtahvayasya prabhō<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrīśākavarṣaṁbulu 1326 gunēṁṭi <unclear>śrā</unclear>
<lb n="5" break="no"/>vaṇa śuddha dvādasi bhṛguvāraṁnāṁḍu patranarāyaṇasamaṁttarā
<lb n="6" break="no"/>yaṁḍu tanaku Abhīṣṭarttasidhigānu śrīnārasiṁhyanāthuniki ni
<lb n="7" break="no"/>tya Ubhayadupalānu parimaṟanu veṁjemarammu kolupulu re 2 sa
<lb n="8" break="no"/>marppiṁpenu Iṁdukai śrībhaḍāramadu padmanidhi gaṁḍama 10 peṭi reṁ
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ḍu kuṁcalu prasādāmu vṛtigāṁ koni sanuluyaṁdu kadiramire
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ḍi kuṁtuṟu tallāsānikini saṁpradāyamaṁdu dōramaseṭṭi siṁgamare
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ḍi kuṁtuṟu pārāsanikini peṭenu vīru Iddaṟu<unclear>nu</unclear> I prasādamu
<lb n="12"/>bhujiṁci I camaralu Ācaṁdrārkkastayigānu koluvaṁgalāru I dha(ra)
<lb n="13" break="no"/><unclear>rmmu</unclear> śrīvaiṣṇava rakṣa śrīśrīśrī
</p>

